<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Both <i>H. macrocarpa </i>and <i>P. radiata </i>are easily killed by fire and typically regenerate from seed in the trees' serotinous cones. They are also capable of seedling establishment with or without crown fire because cones can open on warm days and shed seed without the aid of fire. However, stands of this ruderal alliance typically establish or invade sites after planting, land clearing, grazing, logging, etc.</div>
